      """

Scenario: repoquery --recommends NAMEGLOB-VERSION
 When I execute dnf with args "repoquery --recommends a?-2.0"
 Then the exit code is 0
  And stdout is
      """
      b1 > 1.0
      b2 = 2.0
      """

Scenario: repoquery --recommends NAME (nonexisting package)
